original_title: Bruce Springsteen & The E-Street Band - The 25th Anniversary Rock and Roll Hall of Fame Concerts
overview: The 25th Anniversary Rock and Roll Hall of Fame Concerts were a two-day concert series celebrating the 25th anniversary of the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame . It took place on October 29th and 30th, 2009 at Madison Square Garden
tagline: Bruce Springsteen performs onstage at the 25th Anniversary Rock & Roll Hall of Fame
title: Bruce Springsteen & The E-Street Band - The 25th Anniversary Rock and Roll Hall of Fame Concerts
